  <b>Description</b><br>
This item is dropped by Zordakilicus Ragefire, the new dragon who spawns in Lord Nagafen's Lair. He drops the Blazing Greaves of Fennin Ro, Blazing Boots of Fennin Ro, Blazing Gauntlets of Fennin Ro, the Blazing Vambraces, and Zordakilicus' Heart as his loot. He spawns as part of the clerical epic quest.</td></tr>
